{"id":996,"date":"2017-12-22T08:10:13","date_gmt":"2017-12-22T08:10:13","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/byzan.vn\/?p=996"},"modified":"2022-10-04T08:35:59","modified_gmt":"2022-10-04T01:35:59","slug":"phong-cach-toi-gian-trong-thiet-ke-hien-dai","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/phong-cach-toi-gian-trong-thiet-ke-hien-dai\/","title":{"rendered":"Phong c\u00e1ch t\u1ed1i gi\u1ea3n trong thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><em>Ng\u00e0y c\u00e0ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn cho m\u00ecnh m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng t\u1ed1i gi\u1ea3n. L\u1ed1i s\u1ed1ng \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u00ecn th\u1ea5y qua vi\u1ec7c s\u1ed1ng trong m\u1ed9t c\u0103n nh\u00e0 c\u00f3 ki\u1ebfn tr\u00fac, c\u00e1ch b\u00e0i tr\u00ed n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t t\u1ed1i gi\u1ea3n.<\/em><\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-998\" src=\"http:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/12\/Phong-cach-toi-gian-trong-thiet-ke-hien-dai-3.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1600\" height=\"900\" srcset=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/12\/Phong-cach-toi-gian-trong-thiet-ke-hien-dai-3.jpg 1600w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/12\/Phong-cach-toi-gian-trong-thiet-ke-hien-dai-3-300x169.jpg 300w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/12\/Phong-cach-toi-gian-trong-thiet-ke-hien-dai-3-768x432.jpg 768w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/12\/Phong-cach-toi-gian-trong-thiet-ke-hien-dai-3-1024x576.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1600px) 100vw, 1600px\" \/><\/p>\n<p>H\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf \u0111\u1ed3 \u0111\u1ea1c, b\u1ed1 tr\u00ed h\u1ee3p l\u00fd \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng gian tho\u00e1ng \u0111\u00e3ng h\u01a1n.<\/p>\n<p>Phong c\u00e1ch n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t t\u00f4i gi\u1ea3n l\u00e0 lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf t\u1ed1i \u0111a nh\u1eefng chi ti\u1ebft ph\u00fac t\u1ea1p v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng nh\u1eefng v\u1eadt d\u1ee5ng th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft nh\u1eb1m gi\u1eef \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t kh\u00f4ng gian tr\u1ed1ng ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o. Phong c\u00e1ch t\u1ed1i gi\u1ea3n coi c\u00f4ng n\u0103ng s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng l\u00e0 c\u1ed1t l\u00f5i v\u00e0 g\u1ea1t b\u1ecf t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n r\u01b0\u1eddm r\u00e0, phong c\u00e1ch n\u00e0y ch\u1ee7 y\u1ebfu s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng nh\u1eefng m\u1ea3ng kh\u1ed1i m\u00e0 m\u00e0u s\u1eafc trung t\u00ednh. H\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf \u0111\u1ed3 \u0111\u1ea1c, b\u00e0i tr\u1eeb s\u1ef1 phong ph\u00fa trong trang tr\u00ed.V\u00ec v\u1eady, kh\u00f4ng gian theo phong c\u00e1ch n\u00e0y ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf r\u1ea5t ch\u1eb7t ch\u1ebd v\u1ec1 b\u1ed1 c\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o n\u00ean m\u1ed9t t\u1ed5ng th\u1ec3 th\u1ed1ng nh\u1ea5t, h\u1ee3p l\u00fd, tho\u00e1ng \u0111\u00e3ng v\u00e0 th\u01b0 gi\u00e3n.<\/p>\n<p><strong>Trang tr\u00ed ph\u00f2ng kh\u00e1ch theo phong c\u00e1ch t\u1ed1i gi\u1ea3n<\/strong><\/p>\n<p>N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n mu\u1ed1n l\u00e0m cho kh\u00f4ng gian n\u00e0y th\u00eam \u0111\u1eb9p v\u00e0 r\u1ed9ng r\u00e3i h\u01a1n th\u00ec c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng m\u1ed9t b\u1ed9 sofa g\u00f3c v\u1edbi gam m\u00e0u be n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt. K\u1ebft h\u1ee3p th\u00eam m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i chi\u1ebfc g\u1ed1i t\u1ef1a c\u00f3 c\u00f9ng tone m\u00e0u t\u01b0\u1eddng, b\u1ea1n c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u1ecdn m\u00e0u ghi x\u00e1m \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111em \u0111\u1ebfn cho kh\u00f4ng gian n\u00e0y v\u1ebb \u0111\u1eb9p hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i.<\/p>\n<p class=\"body-text\" style=\"background: white; margin: 0in 0in 11.25pt 0in;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; color: #333333; font-family: 'times new roman', times, serif;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1001\" src=\"http:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/12\/Phong-cach-toi-gian-trong-thiet-ke-hien-dai-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1600\" height=\"950\" srcset=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/12\/Phong-cach-toi-gian-trong-thiet-ke-hien-dai-1.jpg 1600w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/12\/Phong-cach-toi-gian-trong-thiet-ke-hien-dai-1-300x178.jpg 300w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/12\/Phong-cach-toi-gian-trong-thiet-ke-hien-dai-1-768x456.jpg 768w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/12\/Phong-cach-toi-gian-trong-thiet-ke-hien-dai-1-1024x608.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1600px) 100vw, 1600px\" \/><\/span><\/p>\n<p>B\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u1ecdn \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng tr\u1eafng ho\u1eb7c v\u00e0ng cho c\u0103n nh\u00e0 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh b\u1edfi n\u00f3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0m cho c\u0103n nh\u00e0 c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n v\u1ebb \u0111\u1eb9p hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i v\u00e0 b\u1eaft m\u1eaft h\u01a1n.<\/p>\n<p>Trong phong c\u00e1ch t\u1ed1i gi\u1ea3n b\u1ea1n c\u0169ng n\u00ean ch\u00fa \u00fd \u0111\u1ebfn h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng, n\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 quan tr\u1ecdng g\u00f3p ph\u1ea7n l\u00e0m \u0111\u1eb9p v\u00e0 ho\u00e0n thi\u1ec7n kh\u00f4ng gian h\u01a1n.<\/p>\n<p><strong>Ph\u00f2ng \u0103n v\u00e0 ph\u00f2ng b\u1ebfp<\/strong><\/p>\n<p>Ti\u1ebfp n\u1ed1i v\u1edbi ph\u00f2ng kh\u00e1ch l\u00e0 ph\u00f2ng \u0103n. Trong phong c\u00e1ch hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i ph\u00f2ng kh\u00e1ch v\u00e0 ph\u00f2ng \u0103n th\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf theo kh\u00f4ng gian li\u1ec1n m\u1ea1ch, \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y gi\u00fap ph\u00f2ng \u0103n r\u1ed9ng r\u00e3i h\u01a1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u.<\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1003\" src=\"http:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/12\/Phong-cach-toi-gian-trong-thiet-ke-hien-dai.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1600\" height=\"1050\" srcset=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/12\/Phong-cach-toi-gian-trong-thiet-ke-hien-dai.jpg 1600w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/12\/Phong-cach-toi-gian-trong-thiet-ke-hien-dai-300x197.jpg 300w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/12\/Phong-cach-toi-gian-trong-thiet-ke-hien-dai-1024x672.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/12\/Phong-cach-toi-gian-trong-thiet-ke-hien-dai-768x504.jpg 768w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/12\/Phong-cach-toi-gian-trong-thiet-ke-hien-dai-1536x1008.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1600px) 100vw, 1600px\" \/><\/p>\n<p class=\"body-text\" style=\"background: white; margin: 0in 0in 11.25pt 0in;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; color: #333333; font-family: 'times new roman', times, serif;\">\u00a0<\/span>B\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1eb7t ph\u00f2ng b\u1ebfp b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh ph\u00f2ng kh\u00e1ch, v\u1edbi di\u1ec7n t\u00edch c\u0103n nh\u00e0 nh\u1ecf h\u1eb9p n\u00ean b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u1ecdn nh\u1eefng thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf t\u1ee7 \u00e2m t\u01b0\u1eddng v\u1eeba c\u00f3 t\u00e1c d\u1ee5ng n\u1edbi r\u1ed9ng kh\u00f4ng gian l\u1ea1i v\u1eeba gi\u00fap c\u0103n b\u1ebfp th\u00eam g\u1ecdn g\u00e0ng v\u00e0 ti\u1ec7n nghi h\u01a1n.Thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf b\u00e0n \u0103n c\u0169ng gi\u00fap kh\u00f4ng gian \u0103n u\u1ed1ng h\u00e0i h\u00f2a h\u01a1n.<\/p>\n<p>Trang tr\u00ed ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ee7 theo phong c\u00e1ch hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i t\u1ed1i gi\u1ea3n<\/p>\n<p>V\u1edbi thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf h\u00e0i h\u00f2a, m\u1eb7t s\u00e0n r\u1ed9ng ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn \u0111\u00e2y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 \u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf gi\u00fap cho b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t kh\u00f4ng gian ch\u1ee9c n\u0103ng ri\u00eang. B\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p kh\u00f4ng gian n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m n\u01a1i \u0111\u1ecdc s\u00e1ch v\u00e0 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ee7, k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p c\u1ea3 hai b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u0103n ph\u00f2ng ch\u1ee9c n\u0103ng ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o h\u01a1n.<\/p>\n<p class=\"body-text\" style=\"background: white; margin: 0in 0in 11.25pt 0in;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; color: #333333; font-family: 'times new roman', times, serif;\">\u00a0<\/span><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1004\" src=\"http:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/12\/Phong-cach-toi-gian-trong-thiet-ke-hien-dai-2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1600\" height=\"1150\" srcset=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/12\/Phong-cach-toi-gian-trong-thiet-ke-hien-dai-2.jpg 1600w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/12\/Phong-cach-toi-gian-trong-thiet-ke-hien-dai-2-300x216.jpg 300w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/12\/Phong-cach-toi-gian-trong-thiet-ke-hien-dai-2-768x552.jpg 768w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/12\/Phong-cach-toi-gian-trong-thiet-ke-hien-dai-2-1024x736.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1600px) 100vw, 1600px\" \/><\/p>\n<p class=\"body-text\" style=\"background: white; box-sizing: border-box; max-width: 100%; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; widows: 2; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; word-spacing: 0px; margin: 0in 0in 11.25pt 0in;\">T\u00f3m l\u1ea1i, vi\u1ec7c s\u1ed1ng trong m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i nh\u00e0 khang trang, \u0111\u1eb9p \u0111\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng trong cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng c\u1ee7a m\u1ed7i ng\u01b0\u1eddi. N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n \u0111ang c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1ec1 ng\u00f4i nh\u00e0 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, l\u00fac n\u00e0o c\u0169ng c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng khi c\u1ee9 ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i di\u1ec7n v\u1edbi v\u00f4 v\u00e0n c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi nh\u01b0 n\u00ean d\u00f9ng m\u00e0u n\u00e0y, n\u00ean \u0111\u1eb7t v\u1eadt n\u00e0y \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed n\u00e0o l\u00e0 h\u1ee3p l\u00fd\u2026 C\u00e1ch t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n l\u00fac n\u00e0y l\u00e0 gi\u1eef cho n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t \u1edf m\u1ee9c t\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft.<\/p>\n","protected":false